item.description: cdsctl experimental workflow logs download Get the workflow run job status Synopsis Get the workflow run job status cdsctl experimental workflow logs download PROJ_KEY VCS_IDENTIFIER REPO_IDENTIFIER WORKFLOW_NAME RUN-NUMBER [flags] Examples cdsctl experimental workflow logs download <proj_key> <vcs_identifier> <repo_identifier> <workflow_name> <run_number> Options --pattern string Filter on job name Options inherited from parent commands -c, --context string cdsctl context name -f, --file string set configuration file --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers.
